## 🚀 SQL Queries & Executive Insights

### 1️⃣ Product Performance (Volume & Revenue)
* **Objective:** Identify which products drive the highest sales volume and generate the most revenue to optimize inventory.
* **SQL Query:**
```sql
SELECT Product, 
       COUNT(OrderID) AS Total_Orders, 
       SUM(Quantity) AS Total_Quantity_Sold,
       ROUND(SUM(TotalPrice), 2) AS Total_Revenue
FROM Sales
GROUP BY Product
ORDER BY Total_Revenue DESC;
```
* **Output Result:**
| Product | Total_Orders | Total_Quantity_Sold | Total_Revenue ($) |
| :--- | :---: | :---: | :---: |
| Chair | 178 | 562 | 195,620.11 |
