### 5️⃣ High-Value VIP Customers (Advanced HAVING Clause)
* **Objective:** Filter and segment VIP customers whose Customer Lifetime Value (CLV) exceeds $3,000 for targeted loyalty campaigns.
* **SQL Query:**
```sql
SELECT CustomerID, 
       ROUND(SUM(TotalPrice), 2) AS Customer_Lifetime_Value
FROM Sales
GROUP BY CustomerID
HAVING SUM(TotalPrice) > 3000
ORDER BY Customer_Lifetime_Value DESC;
```
